@Vicky1701 this is more a question for spring-cloud as there is no server-side sampling to drop endpoints. I'll give you some hints, but please use gitter for things like this. cheers. https://app.gitter.im/#/room/#openzipkin_zipkin:gitter.im

* spring cloud sleuth has a property https://github.com/openzipkin/brave-example/blob/master/webflux5-sleuth/src/main/resources/application.properties#L16
* if you are using micrometer/spring boot 3, last time I checked, there was no property for sampling, but you can add some code to do it https://github.com/openzipkin/brave-example/blob/master/webflux6-micrometer/src/main/resources/application.yaml#L17-L20
